      • Book

        public Book​(java.lang.String title,
            java.lang.String isbn,
            int pages,
            Genre type,
            Publisher pubs,
            java.lang.String[] author)
        Explicit Value Constructor for a Book.
        Parameters:
        title - Representing the title
        isbn - Representing the isbn
        pages - Representing the total pages in the book
        type - Representing an enumerated type Genre
        pubs - Representing a Publisher reference
        author - Representing an array of Strings which will be converted to Author objects
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if any of the references are null
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if any of the strings are empty or the pages is less than or equal to 0
        NOTE You will not just assign the passed in author array to the class level variable

        pages - Representing the total pages in the book

        pubCity - A String representing the publisher city
        array - Representing an array of Mutable Author objects
        Throws:

        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if any of the strings are empty or the pages is less than or equal to 0
